_sText:
De_Godzilla
-----------
Made by $ol!d$n4k3

Finally it's released. Took half a year, but i didn't work every day on it. 
I just take it easy :) This map is inspired by google earth, 
when i was on google earth and saw all those 3d buildings at the manhattan island. 
i got an idea i'll make this in css, in Godzilla style. And see here what it has become.
There are also some sneaky places in the map. And a plane that can fly try to let it fly :P


UPDATE 
------
i have added HDR and a sound in the background. 
Also changed the poopie brown skybox to Grassy happy rocks.
And changed some couple things more. 
now when you play the map you feel a lot happier :D
